Title: Fixed various dashlet designer position/resizing issues
Level: 2
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.6b1
Date: 1417731747
Class: fix

Previous versions of the dashboard designer had problems with resizing,
moving and changing the anchors of dynamically sized dashlets. Dashlets
were flipping around in different situations and changing sizes in an
unintended way.

All known issues have been fixed now.
